level 3
	proficiency with disguise kit, poisoner's kit
	advantage on creature that hasn't taken turn yet
	any hit against suprised creature counts as a crit

level 9
	infiltration expertise
		new non-combat ability
			cost 7 days, 25 gp to establish history, profession, affiliations for false identity (not real identity of someoen else)

level 13
	imposter
		can spend 3 hours studying a person's speech, writing, and behavior
		indescernable to casual observer
		advantage on deception checks to avoid detection

level 17
	death strike
		when attacking surprised foe
			foe maxes con save (against your dex dc)
			on fail
				damage is doubled
